reviewText: Everyone loves to watch Tom and Jerry at our home!(we have most of their movies). They are always fun to watch.

Tom and Jerry is a classic and still the best show out there. Our whole family loves them and we never tire of them. We keep Tom and Jerry movies in the car (we have four kids) to keep them entertained on car rides. They never tire of them. Fun for everyone!

The best funnies in the movies to be seen and are my favorite.  Simply fun to watch and in every one of the cartoons the action of Tom and Jerry really make me laugh. I have four of their CD'S and would love to have them all. Simply put really funny  actions.
